# PAM configuration for the Metis session lock screen.
#
# Installed to /etc/pam.d/metis. The compositor authenticates the logged-in
# user against this stack when they unlock the screen. It simply defers to the
# system's standard interactive-auth and account stacks, so it honours whatever
# the distro already uses for login (password, fingerprint helpers, etc.).
@include common-auth
@include common-account
